comments.body:
Rather than reading the entire blockfile into memory at once, consider chunking it:

```c++
        size_t left = fs::file_size(file);
        while (left > 0) {
            size_t chunk = std::min<size_t>(left, 2 * MAX_BLOCK_SERIALIZED_SIZE);
            buf.resize(chunk);
            old_blocks.read(buf);
            new_blocks.write_buffer(buf);
            left -= chunk;
        }
```

